Jade Alleyne https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jade_Alleyne 0 Jade Alleyne (born 17 March 2001) is a Scottish-born English actress and singer. She is known for playing the role of Clem Burton in CBBC's 4 O'Clock Club from 2015 to 2017, and for her role as Kaylee in the 2016 Disney Channel UK musical series The Lodge.
